- Add "-showlocation" to eclipse.ini to display workspace location in title bar
- 'Window' --> 'Customize Perspective' to clear out the screen elements. Hide toolbar items, views.
- Debugger
 - F5, F6, F8 -> normal operations
 - 'Display' view to execute adhoc code
 - 'Expression'
 - Drop to Frame - restart from current method (partially)
 
 
